quran[7{c,v,t}:
35,12,"aur pani ke dono zakheeray yaksaa nahi hain aik meetha aur pyaas bujhanay wala hai, peenay mein Khushgawar , aur dosra sakht khaari ke halaq chheel day magar dono se tum tar o taaza gosht haasil karte ho, pahannay ke liye zeenat ka samaan nikaltay ho, aur isi pani mein tum dekhte ho ke kashtiyan uss ka seenah cheerti chali ja rahi hain taakay tum Allah ka fazl talaash karo aur uss ke shukar guzaar bano"
35,13,woh din ke andar raat ko aur raat ke andar din ko pirota howa le aata hai chaand aur Sooraj ko uss ne maskhar kar rakha hai yeh sab kuch aik waqt muqarrar taq chalay ja raha hai wohi Allah ( jis ke yeh saaray kaam hain ) tumhara rab hai badshahi isi ki hai ussay chore kar jin dosaron ko tum pukarte ho woh aik prkah ke maalik bhi nahi hain
35,14,inhen poukaro to woh tumhari duayen sun nahi satke aur sun len to un ka tumhe koi jawab nahi day satke aur qayamat ke roz woh tumahray shirk ka inkaar kar den ge haqeeqat haal ki aisi sahih khabar tumhe aik khabardaar ke siwa koi nahi day sakta
35,15,"logo, tum hi Allah ke mohtaaj ho aur Allah to ghanni o hammeed hai"
35,16,woh chahay to tumhe hata kar koi nai khalqat tumhari jagah le aeye
35,17,aisa karna Allah ke liye kuch bhi dushwaar nahi
35,18,koi boojh uthany wala kisi dosray ka boojh nah uthaye ga aur agar koi lada howa nafs apna boojh uthany ke liye pukare ga to is ke baar ka aik adna hissa bhi btane ke liye koi nah aeye ga chahay woh qareeb tareen rishta daar hi kyun nah ho ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum sirf unhi logon ko mutnabba kar satke ho jo be dekhe apne rab se drtay hain aur namaz qaim karte hain jo shakhs bhi pakizgee ikhtiyar karta hai apni hi bhalai ke liye karta hai aur palatna sab ko Allah hi ki taraf hai
